org.openbel.framework.common.external
Class ReadCache

java.lang.Object
  org.openbel.framework.common.external.ReadCache

public class ReadCache
extends Object

Read operation caching mechanism associated with CachingExternalizable.

This caching mechanism should only be used to cache objects of a specific type.

See Also:
WriteCache
